  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You command your hive to swarm to you or your allies aid. Your hive lands on an ally creature to spit at their injuries with a special saliva to accelerate the healing process.</p><p>Select one creature that you can see within range. When this jutsu is initially cast, that creature regains a number of hit points equal to 3d8. For the duration of the jutsu, the creature regains 1d8 at the start of each of its turn. As a bonus action, you may move the hive to a different ally creature within range.</p><p><strong>At Higher Ranks:</strong> For each rank you cast this jutsu above D-Rank, increase the cost of this jutsu by 3 and increase the healing by +1 die. If this jutsu is cast at B-Rank, you may select a second creature to gain the benefits of this jutsu. At S-Rank, you may select a third creature.</p>",
